#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "Budgets"
msgstr "Proračuni"

#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is a budget?"
msgstr "Kaj je proračun?"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A budget is a categorized list of expected income and expenses for a period."
msgstr ""
"Proračun je kategoriziran seznam pričakovanih prihodkov in odhodkov za "
"določeno obdobje."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Budget facility of &kmymoney; allows you to create annual budgets. More "
"than one Budget can be created for any year. You set monthly Budget values "
"against any Income or Expense categories that you have defined. The values "
"can be set in three ways, depending on the Period:"
msgstr ""
"Proračunska možnost &kmymoney; omogoča ustvarjanje letnih proračunov. Za "
"vsako leto je mogoče ustvariti več kot en proračun. Mesečne vrednosti "
"proračuna nastavite glede na vse kategorije prihodkov ali odhodkov, ki ste "
"jih definirali. Vrednosti je mogoče nastaviti na tri načine, odvisno od "
"obdobja:"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:28 details-budgets.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Monthly"
msgstr "Mesečno"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "(Default) specify a single value applied to every month in the Budget"
msgstr ""
"(Privzeto) določite eno samo vrednost, uporabljeno za vsak mesec v proračunu"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:34 details-budgets.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Yearly"
msgstr "Letno"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify a single value to divide evenly across each month in the Budget"
msgstr ""
"Določite eno samo vrednost, ki jo želite enakomerno razdeliti na vsak mesec "
"v proračunu"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:40 details-budgets.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "Individual"
msgstr "Posameznik"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify separate values for each month."
msgstr "Določite ločene vrednosti za vsak mesec."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used for income and expenses spread irregularly through the year."
msgstr ""
"To se uporablja za prihodke in odhodke, neenakomerno razporejene skozi leto."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; provides a number of reports which compare actual income and "
"expenses against the entered Budgets. These are described in more detail in "
"<link linkend=\"budget.details.reports\">another section</link>."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; ponuja številna poročila, ki primerjajo dejanske prihodke in "
"odhodke z vnesenimi proračuni. Ti so podrobneje opisani v <link linkend="
"\"budget.details.reports\">drugem razdelku</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Your budgets"
msgstr "Vaši proračuni"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can access your budgets in the <guilabel>Budgets View</guilabel>, which "
"you can display by clicking the appropriate icon in the View Selector at the "
"left hand side of your &kmymoney; window."
msgstr ""
"Do svojih proračunov lahko dostopate v <guilabel>pogledu proračunov</"
"guilabel>, ki ga lahko prikažete s klikom na ustrezno ikono v izbirniku "
"pogleda na levi strani vašega okna &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two major sections in the Budgets View. On the left, there is a "
"list of budgets you have created. Above that are buttons for creating, "
"renaming, and deleting budgets. On the right, there are three sections. At "
"the top is the Categories List. At the bottom is a display of the amounts "
"assigned to the budget selected on the left for the category selected in the "
"Categories List above. Between those two areas are some additional controls "
"for managing the budget."
msgstr ""
"V pogledu proračunov sta dva glavna razdelka. Na levi strani je seznam "
"proračunov, ki ste jih ustvarili. Nad tem so gumbi za ustvarjanje, "
"preimenovanje in brisanje proračunov. Na desni strani so trije razdelki. Na "
"vrhu je seznam kategorij. Na dnu je prikaz zneskov, dodeljenih proračunu, "
"izbranem na levi za kategorijo, izbrano na zgornjem seznamu kategorij. Med "
"tema dvema področjema je nekaj dodatnih kontrol za upravljanje proračuna."

#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Viewing, creating, renaming, and deleting budgets"
msgstr "Ogled, ustvarjanje, preimenovanje in brisanje proračunov"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left section of the Budgets View displays the list of Budgets contained "
"in the current &kmymoney; file. If no Budget has yet been created the list "
"will be empty. The list of Budgets has two columns:"
msgstr ""
"Levi del Pogleda proračunov prikazuje seznam proračunov, ki jih vsebuje "
"trenutna datoteka &kmymoney;. Če proračun še ni ustvarjen, bo seznam prazen. "
"Seznam proračunov ima dva stolpca:"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:81 details-budgets.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name of the Budget"
msgstr "Ime proračuna"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Year"
msgstr "Leto"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fiscal year of the Budget. Note that the starting month and day of the "
"fiscal year can be specified in the <link linkend=\"details.settings.general."
"global\">Configure &kmymoney; dialog.</link> To change the fiscal year of a "
"Budget, double click the year."
msgstr ""
"Proračunsko leto proračuna. Upoštevajte, da lahko začetni mesec in dan "
"proračunskega leta določite v dialogu <link linkend=\"details.settings."
"general.global\">Konfiguriraj &kmymoney;.</link> Če želite spremeniti "
"proračunsko leto proračuna, dvokliknite leto."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Values from the selected Budget are displayed to the right. To select a "
"different Budget you can click the budget name in the list on the left. "
"Alternatively, when the list has focus, you can select a different Budget "
"using the &Up; and &Down; keys. If you have made changes to a Budget and "
"then select a different budget, &kmymoney; will ask you whether you want to "
"save or discard the changes."
msgstr ""
"Vrednosti iz izbranega proračuna so prikazane na desni. Če želite izbrati "
"drug proračun, kliknite ime proračuna na seznamu na levi. Ko je seznam v "
"fokusu, lahko izberete drug proračun s tipko &Up; in &Down;. Če ste "
"spremenili proračun in nato izberete drug proračun, &kmymoney; vas bo "
"vprašal, ali želite spremembe shraniti ali zavreči."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are three buttons above the list of Budgets."
msgstr "Nad seznamom proračunov so trije gumbi."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>New</term>"
msgstr "<term>Novo</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a new, empty budget. The default name of a new budget is \"Budget &lt;"
"year&gt;\" where &lt;year&gt; is the current fiscal year."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite nov, prazen proračun. Privzeto ime novega proračuna je »Proračun "
"&lt;leto&gt;« kjer &lt;leto&gt; je tekoče proračunsko leto."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename"
msgstr "Preimenuj"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Edit the name of the selected Budget. You can also edit the name of a Budget "
"by double-clicking the name of a Budget in the list."
msgstr ""
"Uredite ime izbranega proračuna. Ime proračuna lahko uredite tudi tako, da "
"dvokliknete ime proračuna na seznamu."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete"
msgstr "Izbriši"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:136 details-budgets.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete the selected Budget."
msgstr "Izbriši izbrani proračun."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additional options are available on the <guilabel>Budget Options</guilabel> "
"context menu accessed by right-clicking a Budget."
msgstr ""
"Dodatne možnosti so na voljo v kontekstnem meniju <guilabel>Možnosti "
"proračuna</guilabel>, do katerega dostopate z desnim klikom na proračun."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Budget"
msgstr "Nov proračun"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a new, empty Budget."
msgstr "Ustvarite nov, prazen proračun."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename Budget"
msgstr "Preimenuj proračun"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename the selected Budget."
msgstr "Preimenujte izbrani proračun."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete budget"
msgstr "Izbriši proračun"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy budget"
msgstr "Kopiraj proračun"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a copy of the selected Budget. The new Budget has the name \"Copy of "
"&lt;budget&gt;\", where &lt;budget&gt; is the name of the copied Budget."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari kopijo izbranega proračuna. Novi proračun ima ime \"Kopija &lt;"
"proračuna&gt;\", kjer je &lt;proračun&gt; je ime kopiranega proračuna."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "Budget based on forecast"
msgstr "Proračun na podlagi napovedi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fills in budget amounts based on data from &kmymoney;'s Forecast values. See "
"the section on <link linkend=\"details.forecast.define\">Forecasts</link> "
"for more information."
msgstr ""
"Izpolni proračunske zneske na podlagi podatkov iz vrednosti napovedi "
"&kmymoney;. Za več informacij glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"details."
"forecast.define\">Napovedi</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Categories List"
msgstr "Seznam kategorij"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Categories List displays the list of Income and Expense Accounts. "
"(Remember, within &kmymoney;, categories are treated as a special type of "
"account.) As in other places in &kmymoney;, the list is organized in a tree "
"structure. The list can be expanded or collapsed to show or hide "
"Subcategories within a Category. The Categories List has a number of columns:"
msgstr ""
"Seznam kategorij prikazuje seznam računov prihodkov in odhodkov. (Ne "
"pozabite, da se znotraj &kmymoney; kategorije obravnavajo kot posebna vrsta "
"računa.) Kot na drugih mestih v &kmymoney; je seznam organiziran v drevesni "
"strukturi. Seznam je mogoče razširiti ali strniti, da prikažete ali skrijete "
"podkategorije znotraj kategorije. Seznam kategorij ima več stolpcev:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Aside from the Name column, all other columns may be shown or hidden by "
"right-clicking any column header, and checking or unchecking the checkbox "
"next to the column name. For more details about the meaning of each column, "
"see the <link linkend=\"details.categories.view\">Categories View</link> "
"section. Only the columns specifically relevant to Budgets are listed below, "
"but all Category columns may be displayed."
msgstr ""
"Razen stolpca Ime lahko vse druge stolpce prikažete ali skrijete tako, da z "
"desno miškino tipko kliknete glavo stolpca in potrdite ali počistite "
"potrditveno polje poleg imena stolpca. Za več podrobnosti o pomenu vsakega "
"stolpca si oglejte razdelek <link linkend=\"details.categories.view\">Pogled "
"kategorij</link>. Spodaj so navedeni samo stolpci, ki so posebej pomembni za "
"proračune, vendar so lahko prikazani vsi stolpci kategorije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account (Category) name"
msgstr "Ime računa (kategorije)"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Vrsta"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Category Type (Income or Expense)"
msgstr "Vrsta kategorije (prihodek ali odhodek)"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Balance"
msgstr "Stanje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Current balance of Account. This will be blank for Categories, unless the "
"Category is defined in a foreign currency. In this case, Balance will show "
"the value for the Category in its defined currency."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno stanje na računu. Za kategorije bo to prazno, razen če je "
"kategorija definirana v tuji valuti. V tem primeru bo Stanje prikazalo "
"vrednost za kategorijo v njeni definirani valuti."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Total Value"
msgstr "Skupna vrednost"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Total yearly value in the Budget. If a Category has Subcategories and the "
"Category's list of Subcategories is collapsed the value displayed is the sum "
"of the values for the Category and all of its Subcategories. If a Category "
"is defined in a foreign currency, the Total Value will show the value in the "
"base currency."
msgstr ""
"Skupna letna vrednost v proračunu. Če ima kategorija podkategorije in je "
"seznam podkategorij kategorije strnjen, je prikazana vrednost vsota "
"vrednosti za kategorijo in vse njene podkategorije. Če je kategorija "
"definirana v tuji valuti, bo skupna vrednost prikazala vrednost v osnovni "
"valuti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below the Categories List are several controls. The <guiicon> "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-gtk-floppy.svg\" "
"format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> "
"<guibutton>Upd</guibutton> (Update) and <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-edit-undo.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> <guibutton>Res</guibutton> "
"(Reset) buttons are described further below. The <guiicon> "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-zoom-out.svg\" "
"format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guiicon> collapse and "
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-zoom-"
"in.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guiicon> "
"expand buttons collapse or expand the entire Categories List."
msgstr ""
"Pod seznamom kategorij je več kontrolnikov. <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-gtk-floppy.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> <guibutton>Posodobi</guibutton> "
"(Posodobitev) in <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"icon-edit-undo.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> <guibutton>Res</guibutton> (Ponastavi) gumbi "
"so opisani nadalje spodaj. <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"icon-zoom-out.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject></guiicon> strni in <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-zoom-in.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guiicon> gumbi za razširitev strnejo ali "
"razširijo celoten seznam kategorij."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Categories List can be filtered in two ways. Checking the <guilabel>Hide "
"unused budget categories</guilabel> checkbox hides any Categories for which "
"no value has been assigned to the Category or any of its Subcategories in "
"the selected budget. To the right of this, is an unlabelled text box. Only "
"categories which include whatever is typed in this box are listed, but their "
"parent categories are also listed."
msgstr ""
"Seznam kategorij je mogoče filtrirati na dva načina. Če označite potrditveno "
"polje <guilabel>Skrij neuporabljene proračunske kategorije</guilabel>, se "
"skrijejo vse kategorije, ki jim v izbranem proračunu ni bila dodeljena "
"nobena vrednost. Desno od tega je neoznačeno besedilno polje. Navedene so "
"samo kategorije, ki vključujejo vse, kar je vneseno v to polje, navedene pa "
"so tudi njihove nadrejene kategorije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that changing either the <guilabel>Hide unused budget categories</"
"guilabel> or the filter value is likely to change the list of Categories "
"displayed. You may need to re-expand the list to see all the Categories that "
"should be displayed with the current settings."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da bo sprememba bodisi <guilabel>Skrij neuporabljene "
"proračunske kategorije</guilabel> bodisi vrednosti filtra verjetno "
"spremenila seznam prikazanih kategorij. Morda boste morali znova razširiti "
"seznam, da boste videli vse kategorije, ki bi morale biti prikazane s "
"trenutnimi nastavitvami."

#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assignments"
msgstr "Dodelitve"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Assignments area shows the values for the Category selected in the "
"Categories List."
msgstr ""
"Območje Dodelitve prikazuje vrednosti za kategorijo, izbrano na seznamu "
"kategorij."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account"
msgstr "Račun"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name of the selected Category. If the Category is a Subcategory, its "
"full name is displayed in the Category:Subcategory format."
msgstr ""
"Ime izbrane kategorije. Če je kategorija podkategorija, je njeno polno ime "
"prikazano v formatu Kategorija:podkategorija."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Total"
msgstr "Skupaj"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "The total yearly value assigned to the Category."
msgstr "Skupna letna vrednost, dodeljena kategoriji."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include subaccounts"
msgstr "Vključite podračune"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is checked, then Reports show actual income or expenses in "
"Subcategories belonging to the Category against the Category instead of the "
"Subcategory."
msgstr ""
"Če je to označeno, poročila prikazujejo dejanske prihodke ali odhodke v "
"podkategorijah, ki pripadajo kategoriji, v primerjavi s kategorijo namesto s "
"podkategorijo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a Subcategory has a value defined in the Budget, then the income and "
"expenses are shown against the Subcategory."
msgstr ""
"Če ima podkategorija vrednost, določeno v proračunu, so prihodki in odhodki "
"prikazani glede na podkategorijo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the Category selected in the Categories List has its Subcategories "
"collapsed, although its Total Value will show the sum of the Total Values "
"for all its Subcategories, the amounts in the Assignments area may still "
"show 0, unless this box has been checked or an amount has explicitly been "
"assigned to the Category."
msgstr ""
"Če ima kategorija, izbrana na seznamu kategorij, svoje podkategorije "
"strnjene, čeprav bo njena skupna vrednost prikazala vsoto skupnih vrednosti "
"za vse njene podkategorije, lahko zneski v območju Dodelitve še vedno "
"prikazujejo 0, razen če je to polje označeno ali je bil znesek izrecno "
"dodeljen kategoriji."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In general, you will either check this box and assign values to the Category "
"and not to any of its Subcategories, or not check the box, and assign values "
"to the Subcategories but not the Category. If any Subcategories have "
"assigned amounts when this box is checked, then those amounts are rolled up "
"to the Category."
msgstr ""
"Na splošno boste označili to polje in vrednosti dodelili kategoriji in ne "
"kateri koli od njenih podkategorij ali pa polja ne boste označili in "
"vrednosti dodelili podkategorijam, ne pa tudi kategoriji. Če ima katera koli "
"podkategorija dodeljene zneske, ko je to polje označeno, se ti zneski "
"združijo v kategorijo."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clear"
msgstr "Počisti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking this button resets the budgeted category value or values to zero."
msgstr ""
"Klik na ta gumb ponastavi vrednost ali vrednosti proračunske kategorije na "
"nič."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid "Period"
msgstr "Obdobje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This radio buttons allow you to select the period for which the value applies"
msgstr ""
"S temi izbirnimi gumbi lahko izberete obdobje, za katero velja vrednost"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A single value is entered, specifying the amount per month. This is the "
"default setting."
msgstr ""
"Vnese se ena vrednost, ki določa znesek na mesec. To je privzeta nastavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid "A single value is entered, specifying the amount per year."
msgstr "Vnese se ena vrednost, ki določa znesek na leto."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Values are specified for each Calendar month. This is used where expense or "
"income is spread irregularly through the year."
msgstr ""
"Vrednosti so določene za vsak koledarski mesec. To se uporablja, kadar so "
"odhodki ali prihodki neenakomerno porazdeljeni skozi leto."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a value is or values are already specified and the Period is changed, "
"&kmymoney; will ask whether to use the current total yearly value to assign "
"the new values."
msgstr ""
"Če je vrednost ali so vrednosti že določene in je obdobje spremenjeno, bo "
"&kmymoney; vprašal, ali naj uporabi trenutno skupno letno vrednost za "
"dodelitev novih vrednosti."

#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Update and Revert"
msgstr "Posodobi in razveljavi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a Budget's values are first modified, the <guibutton>Update</guibutton> "
"and <guibutton>Revert</guibutton> buttons are enabled. Multiple changes can "
"be made to the Budget. Pressing <guibutton>Update</guibutton> will store the "
"changes and disable these buttons."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vrednosti proračuna prvič spremenjene, sta omogočena gumba "
"<guibutton>Posodobi</guibutton> in <guibutton>Povrni</guibutton>. V proračun "
"je mogoče narediti več sprememb. Če pritisnete <guibutton>Posodobi</"
"guibutton>, boste shranili spremembe in onemogočili te gumbe."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Save</guibutton> button only saves changes that have been "
"stored using the <guibutton>Update</guibutton> button. Thus, if you have "
"modified a Budget but not yet stored the changes <guibutton>Save</guibutton> "
"button will not affect the modified Budget and the <guibutton>Update</"
"guibutton> and <guibutton>Revert</guibutton> buttons remain enabled."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Shrani</guibutton> shrani le spremembe, ki so bile shranjene "
"z gumbom <guibutton>Posodobi</guibutton>. Torej, če ste spremenili proračun, "
"vendar še niste shranili sprememb, gumb <guibutton>Shrani</guibutton> ne bo "
"vplival na spremenjeni proračun, gumba <guibutton>Posodobi</guibutton> in "
"<guibutton>Povrni</guibutton> pa ostaneta omogočeno."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Revert undoes any changes made to a Budget since the last Update and "
"disables the <guibutton>Update</guibutton> and <guibutton>Revert</guibutton> "
"buttons."
msgstr ""
"Razveljavi razveljavi vse spremembe proračuna od zadnje posodobitve in "
"onemogoči gumba <guibutton>Posodobi</guibutton> in <guibutton>Povrni</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "Budget Reports"
msgstr "Poročila o proračunu"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; provides a number of reports to compare actual income and "
"expenses against a Budget. These are listed in Reports under \"Budgeting\". "
"There are two types of Budget Reports:"
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; nudi številna poročila za primerjavo dejanskih prihodkov in "
"odhodkov s proračunom. Ti so navedeni v poročilih pod \"Proračun\". "
"Obstajata dve vrsti poročil o proračunu:"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid "Budget only"
msgstr "Samo proračun"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "These reports display values from a Budget."
msgstr "Ta poročila prikazujejo vrednosti iz proračuna."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid "Monthly Budget"
msgstr "Mesečni proračun"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays the monthly values from a Budget."
msgstr "Prikaže mesečne vrednosti iz proračuna."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid "Yearly Budget"
msgstr "Letni proračun"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays the monthly values from a Budget, with yearly total."
msgstr "Prikaže mesečne vrednosti iz proračuna z letnim zneskom."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid "Budget vs. Actual"
msgstr "Proračun v primerjavi z dejanskim"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These reports compare values from a Budget to actual income and expenses. In "
"each budget report you can find the columns Budget, Actual, and Difference. "
"Each report differs in the period that is shown."
msgstr ""
"Ta poročila primerjajo vrednosti iz proračuna z dejanskimi prihodki in "
"odhodki. V vsakem proračunskem poročilu najdete stolpce Proračun, Dejansko "
"in Razlika. Vsako poročilo se razlikuje glede na prikazano obdobje."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "Budget vs. Actual This Year"
msgstr "Proračun v primerjavi z dejanskim letos"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the beginning of the year until today"
msgstr "Od začetka leta do danes"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "Budget vs. Actual This Year (YTM)"
msgstr "Proračun v primerjavi z dejanskim letos (YTM)"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the beginning of the year until the last day of the previous month"
msgstr "Od začetka leta do zadnjega dne prejšnjega meseca"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Monthly Budgeted vs. Actual"
msgstr "Mesečno predvideno v primerjavi z dejanskim"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the beginning of the year until the last day of the current month"
msgstr "Od začetka leta do zadnjega dne tekočega meseca"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Yearly Budgeted vs. Actual"
msgstr "Letni proračun v primerjavi z dejanskim"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid "From January 1st until December 31st"
msgstr "Od 1. januarja do 31. decembra"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Yearly Budgeted vs. Actual (Graph)"
msgstr "Letni proračun v primerjavi z dejanskim (graf)"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid "Same as the previous report but it shows the graph by default"
msgstr "Enako kot prejšnje poročilo, vendar privzeto prikazuje graf"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These reports provide a base from which custom reports can be created by "
"changing the date range and Budget, among other options."
msgstr ""
"Ta poročila zagotavljajo osnovo, iz katere je mogoče ustvariti poročila po "
"meri, tako da med drugimi možnostmi spremenite časovno obdobje in proračun."

#~ msgid "2011-06-29"
#~ msgstr "29.06.2011"

#~ msgid "<releaseinfo>4.6</releaseinfo>"
#~ msgstr "<releaseinfo>4.6</releaseinfo>"

#~ msgid "Edit the name of the selected Budget."
#~ msgstr "Uredite ime izbranega proračuna."

#~ msgid "Change budget year"
#~ msgstr "Spremenite proračunsko leto"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Displays a window with a list of years to select a different fiscal year "
#~ "for the budget."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Prikaže okno s seznamom let za izbiro drugega proračunskega leta za "
#~ "proračun."

#~ msgid "Account List"
#~ msgstr "Seznam računov"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Below the Accounts List are several controls. The <guibutton>Update</"
#~ "guibutton> and <guibutton>Revert</guibutton> buttons are described "
#~ "further below. The collapse and expand buttons collapse or expand the "
#~ "entire Accounts List."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Pod seznamom računov je več kontrolnikov. Gumba <guibutton>Posodobi</"
#~ "guibutton> in <guibutton>Povrni</guibutton> sta podrobneje opisana "
#~ "spodaj. Gumba za strnitev in razširitev strneta ali razširita celoten "
#~ "seznam računov."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "For performance reasons, changes made to a Budget are not saved "
#~ "immediately. Instead, they must first be stored using the "
#~ "<guibutton>Update</guibutton> button and then permanently saved using the "
#~ "<guibutton>Save</guibutton> button."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Zaradi učinkovitosti se spremembe proračuna ne shranijo takoj. Namesto "
#~ "tega jih je treba najprej shraniti z gumbom <guibutton>Posodobi</"
#~ "guibutton> in nato trajno shraniti z gumbom <guibutton>Shrani</guibutton>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Changes stored using <guibutton>Update</guibutton> but not yet saved "
#~ "using <guibutton>Save</guibutton> can only be reverted by reloading the "
#~ "&kmymoney; file."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Spremembe, shranjene z <guibutton>Posodobi</guibutton>, vendar še ne "
#~ "shranjene z <guibutton>Shrani</guibutton>, je mogoče razveljaviti samo s "
#~ "ponovnim nalaganjem datoteke &kmymoney; mapa."
